{"id": 1375, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在工作 or 学习的时候有哪些作作的习惯？", "description": "越是不想干活儿的时候，对仪式感的追求就越强烈。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6412, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170322103347MsxuN98rGwmbYj4t.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-15T03:10:09Z", "options": [{"id": 144384, "content": "一上班就认真学习，沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620309}, {"id": 145665, "content": "先泡一杯茶，倒个水。看个漫画", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 827584}, {"id": 151553, "content": "玩头发，咬笔头", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893260}, {"id": 178433, "content": "自己一个人不想学习，要有别人在，而且要别人安安静静的不要发出声音，才能静下心来搞学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969556}, {"id": 144386, "content": "喜欢一个人～太多人在一起静不下心～还需配音乐和零食", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756458}, {"id": 144387, "content": "喜欢喝茶，哪怕是袋泡茶。泡上茶才能安静下来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852689}, {"id": 145923, "content": "会买杯喝的说边写边喝，结果工作还没开始往往就喝完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875340}, {"id": 149763, "content": "一定要把所有相关书全拿出来才能学习……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886672}, {"id": 154883, "content": "扎头发，戴眼镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683449}, {"id": 197380, "content": "进入状态就没有了时间观念 没进入状态就时间观念超强", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014928}, {"id": 144388, "content": "查一遍所有的邮箱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758749}, {"id": 145924, "content": "提前睡十分钟，养精蓄锐?\nQADYQWAN 我微信", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875338}, {"id": 144389, "content": "不到最后一刻，绝不动手。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867703}, {"id": 145157, "content": "爱抠手 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872179}, {"id": 164101, "content": "要么精力超级集中，要么超不集中", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930242}, {"id": 260869, "content": "吃饭必须看视频", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212130}, {"id": 144390, "content": "学习时候，书桌上绝对不能放任何事物！而且必须先收拾干净，什么都没有，除了电脑。当然，学起来了，需要的书，有联系的书全都招呼过来！嗯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321645}, {"id": 150022, "content": "学习前早早想好几点结束", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695735}, {"id": 152070, "content": "总是想看手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897997}, {"id": 144391, "content": "桌面必须有大片留白", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680452}, {"id": 145159, "content": "不找到一首合适的歌就没法开始学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850292}, {"id": 174599, "content": "在脑子里安排好所有的计划   如果被打乱又会再重新来一遍  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957757}, {"id": 144392, "content": "一定要有节点！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087449}, {"id": 144393, "content": "听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860410}, {"id": 144394, "content": "水杯里一定要有满满的热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807504}, {"id": 144906, "content": "学习的时候环境的光线和温度必须舒服才能开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871103}, {"id": 230922, "content": "听着歌才能专注学习，不听歌学习学一会就总想动动这个动动那个", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111150}, {"id": 178186, "content": "抖腿，不停的抖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98400}, {"id": 144395, "content": "打开镜子...", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 44889}, {"id": 145163, "content": "转笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872201}, {"id": 145931, "content": "一边做着事一边手摸去手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875385}, {"id": 151819, "content": "必须用手机听歌或者手机要放在看得见摸得着的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896818}, {"id": 152331, "content": "带耳夹，看书，写作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898956}, {"id": 226571, "content": "手机没电了再学习吧！……充着电再玩会吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094184}, {"id": 261131, "content": "看数学书，只要是晚上无论在什么场所，不超过十分钟，就会睡觉?，而且睡的超级香", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241616}, {"id": 144396, "content": "听音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867820}, {"id": 144908, "content": "一定要放一首古典音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871258}, {"id": 144397, "content": "拔头发。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267539}, {"id": 144909, "content": "一定要放一首古典音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871258}, {"id": 219405, "content": "想好了才开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069400}, {"id": 178445, "content": "做计算题的时候嘴巴里一定要嚼糖果", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969629}, {"id": 144398, "content": "戴上耳机听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247727}, {"id": 144399, "content": "想着要如何专注", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867051}, {"id": 145679, "content": "动笔学习写作业前，一定要把手洗干净，不然总觉得哪里不舒服。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874081}, {"id": 177935, "content": "流程强迫症 绝不更改", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967859}, {"id": 173840, "content": "永远也提不起精神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955524}, {"id": 202769, "content": "一定会挨到整点开始动，学习一定要在图书馆，看书一定要在床前，工作一定要开台灯，写不出材料必吃辣条喝咖啡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029436}, {"id": 144401, "content": "写英文", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 435399}, {"id": 144657, "content": "要整理的干干净净在开始学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869675}, {"id": 145681, "content": "到该考核或考试的时候才想起来去做", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874090}]}